Class GraphElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.common.model.impl.pojo.Element
      • org.gradoop.common.model.impl.pojo.GraphElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, EPGMAttributed, EPGMElement, EPGMGraphElement, EPGMIdentifiable, EPGMLabeled
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Edge, Vertex

    public abstract class GraphElement
extends Element
implements EPGMGraphElement
    Abstract class representing an EPGM element that is contained in a logical graph (i.e. vertices and edges).
